sequenceDiagram
    title UC-07 View History
    actor User
    participant UI as HistoryScreen (UI)
    participant VM as HistoryViewModel
    participant Repo as AuditRepository
    participant Nav as AppNav

    User ->> UI: user opens History
    UI ->> VM: open History
    VM ->> Repo: getHistory()
    alt No audits found
        Repo ->> VM: List is empty
        VM ->> UI: show "No reports yet"
    else Audits found
        Repo ->> VM: List<Audit>
    end
    VM ->> UI: display past audits (newest first)

    User ->> UI: selects Audit from History
    UI ->> VM: selects Audit
    VM ->> Nav: navigateToReportScreen()